  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;ve been getting back to writing in Emacs and just got to the point where I can publish my personal website from my files.\nHere\u0026rsquo;s me babbling about that: Babble, [2025-08-22 Fri 22:41]\nIt\u0026rsquo;ll take a while for there to be enough information on the site for it to be useful to anyone, but I just wanted to post again about how happy I am to have a computer that can actually run Emacs and do some SQLite stuff without choking.\n",
